Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Fiore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A neutral country of 17 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a world of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is bought and sold there every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an integral part of people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are those who use magic as their occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are referred to as wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:34.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wizards belong to various guilds \Nand perform jobs on commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:38.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a large number of guilds within the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a certain city there lies a certain guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:49.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild from which various legends were once born... Or \Nrather, will continue to be born long into the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And its name is:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:55.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:06.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:16.13,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Can you hear this voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:21.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! It's hoarse from yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:25.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Until your heart can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:29.48,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:34.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon and sun high-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:39.18,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:44.58,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're not here to make me laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.72,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,even what I'm looking for can't be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:51.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowing, be honest with yourself and smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:56.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,because when two people lay close, time overlaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:07.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:30.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisenwald is plotting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami Erigor, the "Death God." {I'll stick this in here as an inline note, I think it's not too obtrusive}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some fly from a legal guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that flute! It's the flute of curse, Lullaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:52.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Clover, where the Guildmaster\NLeague is holding their regular meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:59.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov, deary, it sure must be nice to have \Nall your little wizardies so pepped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master of the Blue Pegasus guild, Bob.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:06.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,FYI, a man. {perhaps out of character? In that case "incidentally" would work, but it's less funny}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:11.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, I heard that you gave some aristocrat a thrashing. {Yeah, that's what he's talking about}{I presume he's referring to Everlue, hence my use of powerbroker... maybe better word here?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:13.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was my new recruit, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.78,0:03:15.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:17.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a boyoyoing figure she's got! {it isn't the same gag. "boyoyon" is "bouncy"}{keeping the running gag...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you flirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this something to be laughing about, Makarov?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:28.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master of the Quatro Cerberus guild, Goldmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:32.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's great they're energetic, but they go way overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:39.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people on the council who're worried Fairy \NTail's gonna crush an entire city one day, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to be crushed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:44.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...by Lucy's body, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:45.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's not proper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go laying hands on your own little wizardies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Makarov!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:51.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Makarov!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter from Ms. Mirajane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:54.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:55.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, hard at work at your regular meeting, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:04.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This here's our poster-girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:08.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a looker, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:11.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Mirajane, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure looks like she's grown up... {No, she was a much more terrifying wizard when she was younger}{I'm being careful here because maybe she only LOOKS like she's grown...}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:20.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, something wonderful happened while you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:24.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazingly, Natsu, Gray, and Erza formed a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:28.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is the most powerful team in all of Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:32.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I should report this, so I wrote you a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:36.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:41.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems those worries might actually come to pass, oy... {Are you sure you want yiddish in there? In Japanese, "oy" is just another word for "hey"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:45.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:48.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys might actually be able to destroy an entire city!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:53.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The regular meeting's over today, and I'm returning tomorrow, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:57.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let nothing happen until then, I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:02.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairies in the Wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunugi station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:10.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy with a giant sickle barged on board all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:15.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're those bastards from the dark guild that hangs around this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:19.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could understand getting on a cart or a boat, but a train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:23.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! {whoa, Happy said "hai!"}What's the benefit of escaping on a train that can only run on rails?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fast, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:32.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys from Eisenwald must be in a big hurry for some reason then, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:33.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you strip?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:34.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the army's already on the move...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it only a matter of time until they're caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be nice, if it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:54.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A fly from Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:56.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you let him see the Lullaby flute and get away without saying a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kageyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like our plan is blown!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:05.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if he did notice, it's not like anyone could stop us now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.21,0:06:11.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is important that we take extra precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:13.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to put {\i1}that{\i0} plan into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, at Oshibana station...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:19.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a forest the flies cannot be allowed to buzz around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach them all a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:22.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:27.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, you're going too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:30.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the SE plug is inflating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:34.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let that flute be played, a great number of innocent people will be victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:37.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by hearing the sound, a person's life is stolen from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:41.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to do when we get there, and you don't have any magical power left?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens then I'll fight with a stick if I have too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you two are here, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:51.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling I should say something to you, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To me? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:58.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot. I just know it had something to do with you, Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:00.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna hurl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:01.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:03.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Natsu! You'll fall out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, what was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:13.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not "Lucy, gonna barf..." then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:17.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish are yummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Healthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:21.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird... Weird... Weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying I'm weird already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshibana station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There has been a train derailment! We can't let you into the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:35.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A train derailed? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear rumors that some dangerous guys are holed up in the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You! What's the situation inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:45.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the situation inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the situation inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:50.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess she doesn't have use for people who don't answer promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:53.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand what Erza's like, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you strip?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:55.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisenwald's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:56.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:59.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this one my responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:07:59.37,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}This one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:02.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:08.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An army platoon stormed in, but it seems they haven't returned yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:12.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's likely that they engaged Eisenwald in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They were up against an entire guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single one of them are wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An army platoon hardly stood a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:36.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You Fairy Tail Flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how many there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend! So you're Erigor, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:55.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance. Trains, 4-wheelers, Lucys...  {the plurals make it funnier}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's motion sickness times three!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm transportation now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:04.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault master Erigor got angry at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you scoundrels after?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do with the Lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.89,0:09:12.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's here at the train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:17.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Wind Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan on broadcasting the Lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:29.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many thousands of onlookers are gathered around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:33.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you increase the volume, it'll reverberate throughout the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The melody of death, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:40.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan on making innocent people listen to the flute's lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:46.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm purging the fools who guard their own rights and safety
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:50.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,without even knowing there are those whose same rights have been stolen away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:55.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their sin is living without knowing that this world isn't just.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:55.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:58.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinigami has come to punish them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to get your rights back by doing something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:07.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And weren't you thrown out of the league because you did a ton of bad stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:10.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've come this far, we don't want rights anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:11.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:16.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those with power can wipe the past clean, and can rule the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a complete idiot, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:21.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you, flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get to see the new dark age because you're heading to the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:35.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that voice {\i1}was{\i0} you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.98,0:10:38.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's back in the nick of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:42.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There's a bunch of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemies, every last one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:48.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell right into my trap, Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:02.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going exactly as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:06.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some bastards that I must make sure hear this flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:09.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to pay them back for what they did! {too many bastards too close together}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fairy Tail's strongest team!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:15.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them see how fearsome a dark guild really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You two head after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:29.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you two work together, there's no way you'd lose, even to the "death god" Erigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:34.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:34.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They ran off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to follow Erigor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Rayure, will bring them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:44.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.62,0:11:47.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive that bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:51.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After we clean up these guys, we're heading after them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two girls against this many?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:58.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two girls? What do you think you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:02.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna pluck off your wings, fly-babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're so cute... You wouldn't dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:08.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wretches! {or less midieval, "lowlifes!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:16.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One more insult to Fairy Tail, and I can't guarantee you'll live to see tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't nothing we ain't seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:27.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We gots plenty of our own magic swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how 'bout some of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It turned into a spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:54.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pair of swords this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:57.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman... She can requip so fast! {I coined "Requip Magic" in the manga -- I guess it never got to the glossary}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:02.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic swords are similar to your Celestial magic, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:06.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It works where you call out weapons that are stored in an alternate space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Switching out which weapon you have is called "Requipping."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:14.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's just getting warmed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I can fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:21.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? This was supposed to be Erza's highlight scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:28.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Giant Crab, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also a fight this time-ebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut this fight short, would you? {I switched the meaning  slightly to keep the barber pun...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:50.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You with the freakish hairdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get you good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:57.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:13:59.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:00.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kappa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:01.36,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kappa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice cut-ebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:06.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, it wasn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I made a good impression!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was your goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the way he ends his sentences intrigues me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:21.08,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Digression
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"-Ebi?" I just don't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:17.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At least say "-snip" or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:19.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ebi-snip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway... {look up}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:27.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are still so many left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:28.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:29.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wipe them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:48.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, her armor's coming off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:53.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights usually fight by requipping different weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:15:00.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Erza has increased her own abilities, and can fight while requipping different magic armor as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Erza's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:06.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called: The Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance, my blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:13.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Circle Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:23.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She wiped most of them out in a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:24.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:25.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:29.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:32.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the most powerful woman in Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:40.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fairy Queen, Titania Erza! {Nope. Just a reference to the Spencer's "The Fairie Queen" -- It's just a nickname} {I presume this is the country she's from?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:47.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:49.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going up against that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be heading towards Erigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:54.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:55.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:56.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:06.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must've driven that magic 4-wheeler too fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, the rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Work together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:14.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:17.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire and ice don't help each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:20.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And man, that Erza just does whatever she wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:23.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She decides everything herself, no questions asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle this Erigor person perfectly fine by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:26.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle this Erigor person perfectly fine by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't copy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't copy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:31.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:33.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we should split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:41.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, we're up against someone who's trying to let loose some seriously dangerous magic here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:43.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find him, give him a thrashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:48.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And not only that, he picked a fight with Fairy Tail. What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll burn him to a smoldering crisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you die on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:16:59.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:11.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... If he was planning on broadcasting the lullaby...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:14.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The broadcast booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:25.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So then he isn't planning on broadcasting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:33.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd come here trying to mess up our plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:36.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So what're you guys {\i1}really{\i0} planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:44.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:48.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you value your lives, get away from here immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This station has been taken over by evil wizards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:57.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And those wizards are attempting to perform magic that will kill every person here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:59.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuate as far away from here as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:07.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Why'd you make everyone panic like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:09.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than them all becoming victims, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:12.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You people should evacuate as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:19.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there are no longer people around the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:21.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do now, Erigor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:23.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:27.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The station is being surrounded by wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:35.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can escape from my urumi! {http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Urumi}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:48.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Magic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:53.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:59.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you bastards really after?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:03.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not planning on playing the lullaby over the loud speakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:08.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erigor's magic wind wall should be in place by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic wind wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:14.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A barrier of wind so that none of you idiots can escape from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:19.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I always did want to fight you once, Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But alas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time to play with you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.03,0:19:29.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erigor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even try.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:37.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This magic wind wall is one-way: you can only pass from outside to inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:41.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to exit from the inside, the wind will cut you to shreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:43.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:47.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you idiots I've wasted quite a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:50.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:55.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Erigor... Where could he be heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:20:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So he wasn't targeting this station after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:04.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of your riddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:06.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain what's going on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:10.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We just made a cage to trap you flies is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:18.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were only taking over this station to block the route to the end of the line, Clover station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:22.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Clover station is across a giant gorge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:26.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to get there except this route.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:30.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you can fly like Erigor, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:32.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's where you're going to use Lullaby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:34.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what's at Clover station?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:37.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Try and recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:40.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:45.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Clover... That's the town where the old men are having their regular meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your true objectives are the guild masters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:53.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've finally noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:57.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A bit slow on the uptake, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:21:01.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those old men are extremely powerful wizards... Pretty bold of you, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:06.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a piece of cake to make those unsuspecting codgers listen to the flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:10.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know master Erigor will be able to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:15.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you pests won't stop us! You can't leave this station!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:17.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:21.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get our revenge on those people who oppressed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:24.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wipe them all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:41.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll make you pay for targeting our master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:46.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those old men are like our parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:55.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about time to spring the trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erigor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:02.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that fat one go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:05.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't find him, Erza will throttle you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:13.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show you there're guilds {\i1}way{\i0} scarier than any dark guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:28.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me away to someplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:33.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride on a tin horse, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:36.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.47,0:22:44.06,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad that my beloved doll can't talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:46.43,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:51.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I think of you tears start to flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:56.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a crybaby, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:59.46,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,In the moon (the moon) at night (at night)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:01.20,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always (I'm always)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:04.50,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,searching for the rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:07.18,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:09.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,so much it's like I'm under a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:12.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This love is a monologue
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:15.11,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,from which I'll never awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:17.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:20.34,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,since I've completely fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:23.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what spell I could chant,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:25.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to get through to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.56,0:23:29.51,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Spouting this and that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:36.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just love you like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:39.28,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,One day I want to be able to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:41.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"You got me."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:45.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,My words of thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:54.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.34,0:23:59.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza looked so cool in her armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:02.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she's got over a hundred different types.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.16,0:24:07.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had cool armor like some heroic warrior of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.33,0:24:11.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you look better in other outfits, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:13.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.67,0:24:16.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Flame and Wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.15,0:24:18.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone likes that outfit the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.46,0:24:19.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some uniform or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.10,0:24:21.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.22,0:24:22.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That maid out-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give the maid jokes a rest already!
